flowchart TD
    A[Page Makes fetch Request] --> B[Service Worker fetch Handler Intercepts]
    B --> C{Resource type?}
    C -- Static app shell --> D[Cache-First Strategy]
    C -- API data --> E[Network-First Strategy]
    C -- Semi-static content --> F[Stale-While-Revalidate Strategy]
    D --> G{Cache has entry?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Serve from Cache Immediately]
    H --> I[Update Cache in Background if Network Available]
    G -- No --> J[Fetch from Network and Cache Result]
    E --> K{Network available?}
    K -- Yes --> L[Fetch from Network]
    L --> M[Update Cache with Fresh Response]
    K -- No --> N{Cache has stale entry?}
    N -- Yes --> O[Serve Stale Cache Entry]
    N -- No --> P[Return Offline Fallback Page]
    F --> Q[Serve from Cache Immediately]
    Q --> R[Revalidate from Network in Background]
    R --> S[Update Cache with Fresh Data]
    style H fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
    style O fill:#f59e0b,color:#fff
    style P fill:#ef4444,color:#fff
